distributing any covered work, you accept all terms herein.

1. DEFINITIONS

   a. "Software" refers to any source code, compiled binaries, scripts,
      assets, or logic files distributed under this license.

   b. "Web Application" (Web App) refers to any browser-based or
      server-side application, including but not limited to websites,
      progressive web apps (PWAs), APIs, dashboards, and online tools,
      distributed or derived from works under this license.

   c. "AI-Assisted Work" refers to any software, web app, text, design,
      logic, or creative output that was generated in whole or in part
      with the assistance of artificial intelligence tools (e.g., large
      language models, code generators, image generators), where the
      original prompting, direction, curation, or integration was
      performed by the copyright holder.

   d. "Covered Work" means the Software, Web Application, AI-Assisted
      Work, or any combination or derivative thereof.

   e. "You" refers to any individual or legal entity exercising rights
      under this license.

